name: Aries in its power color
description:
Go out and take on the world with your zodiac power color that amplifies your inherent nature and boosts your confidence to express yourself more freely.  

Big, bold, and in charge, Aries feels most empowered by red. “Aries is ruled by the planet Mars, which, in medical astrology, is in charge of adrenal glands and blood, among other things,” Terrones explains. “So red is the perfect color for Aries, as it represents their ability to react well in high-pressure situations and to enjoy the adrenaline that comes with adventure.” Amplify your courage and presence as a leader through this dominant color, whether you’re working, working out, or embarking on a new adventure.
